name: Ultra Suede Sculpting Lip Pencil
description: The Ultra Suede Sculpting Lip Pencil defines and shapes lips with a smooth, creamy matte formula that feels comfortable all day. Its lip-lock technology prevents feathering, keeping your look precise and long-lasting. A built-in brush blends color seamlessly for a polished, sophisticated finish.

name: Blur HD Setting Powder
description: A weightless, ultra-fine loose powder that perfects and sets your makeup with a soft matte or radiant finish. The silky texture blurs the look of pores and fine lines while controlling shineâ€”without ever feeling dry or cakey. Infused with vitamins C and E plus oil-absorbing minerals, it keeps your complexion smooth, fresh, and photo-ready from day to night. Available in multiple shades for every skin tone.

name: Supreme Lash Volumizing Mascara
description: Amplify your lashes with this ultra-black, buildable mascara that delivers dramatic volume and length without clumping or flaking. The precision brush coats every lash from root to tip, creating a bold, eye-opening effect that lasts all day. Perfect for achieving a full, fluttery look with just a few swipes.

name: Luxe Velvet Matte Lipstick
description: Indulge in rich, velvety color that glides on effortlessly and stays put for hours. This luxurious matte lipstick delivers full-coverage pigment with a soft, comfortable formula that won't dry out your lips. Available in a stunning range of shades to suit every mood and occasion.

name: Radiant Glow Highlighter Palette
description: Illuminate your features with this versatile highlighter palette featuring four complementary shades. From subtle shimmer to intense glow, these silky powders blend seamlessly onto your skin for a luminous, lit-from-within radiance. Perfect for highlighting cheekbones, brow bones, and cupid's bow.

name: Precision Wing Eyeliner Pen
description: Create flawless winged liner with this ultra-fine felt tip pen that delivers intense black pigment in one smooth stroke. The quick-drying, smudge-proof formula ensures your liner stays sharp and precise all day, while the ergonomic grip gives you total control for any eye look.

name: Flawless Finish Foundation
description: Achieve a natural, airbrushed complexion with this lightweight, buildable foundation that adapts to your skin tone. The long-wearing formula provides medium to full coverage while letting your skin breathe, controlling oil, and blurring imperfections for a smooth, even finish that lasts up to 24 hours.

name: Sculpt & Define Contour Kit
description: Master the art of contouring with this expertly curated palette featuring six shades for sculpting, bronzing, and highlighting. The creamy, blendable formula effortlessly defines your features for a chiseled, dimensional look. Includes a step-by-step guide for professional results at home.

name: Hydrating Lip Gloss Trio
description: Get juicy, high-shine lips with this trio of nourishing glosses in universally flattering shades. Enriched with vitamin E and natural oils, each gloss hydrates while delivering a lustrous, non-sticky finish. Wear alone for a natural pop of color or layer over lipstick for extra dimension.

name: Ultimate Eye Shadow Palette
description: Unleash your creativity with this 35-shade palette featuring a mix of matte, shimmer, and metallic finishes. From everyday neutrals to bold statement colors, these highly pigmented shadows blend effortlessly and last all day. Includes a dual-ended brush for easy application on the go.

name: Brow Perfection Pencil & Gel Duo
description: Frame your face with perfectly sculpted brows using this two-in-one product. The precision pencil fills in sparse areas with natural-looking strokes, while the tinted gel sets and holds hairs in place all day. Available in multiple shades to match every hair color.

name: Blush & Bronze Duo
description: Add warmth and dimension to your complexion with this dynamic duo. The silky blush delivers a natural flush of color, while the bronzer gives you a sun-kissed glow. Both shades blend seamlessly and work beautifully on all skin tones for a healthy, radiant finish.

name: Color Correcting Concealer Palette
description: Neutralize dark circles, redness, and discoloration with this five-shade concealer palette. Each color-correcting hue targets specific concerns, while the creamy formula blends effortlessly to create a flawless base. Includes a mirror and application guide for perfect coverage every time.

name: Lash & Brow Growth Serum
description: Promote fuller, longer lashes and brows with this nourishing serum packed with peptides, biotin, and natural botanicals. The gentle formula strengthens hair follicles and encourages healthy growth for visibly thicker, more defined lashes and brows in as little as 4 weeks.

name: Makeup Setting Spray
description: Lock in your look with this ultra-fine setting spray that keeps makeup fresh and flawless for up to 16 hours. The lightweight mist controls oil and shine while preventing fading, creasing, or settling into fine lines. Infused with skin-loving ingredients for a comfortable, breathable finish.

name: Cream Blush & Lip Tint Stick
description: Get a coordinated, natural flush with this multi-purpose cream stick that works on both cheeks and lips. The buildable formula blends seamlessly into skin for a dewy, healthy glow that lasts all day. Perfect for quick touch-ups and on-the-go beauty.

name: Waterproof Gel Eyeliner Pot
description: Create bold, dramatic eye looks with this long-lasting gel eyeliner that glides on smoothly and sets to a waterproof finish. The intensely pigmented formula won't smudge, fade, or transfer throughout the day. Includes a precision brush for perfect application every time.

name: HD Makeup Sponge Set
description: Achieve a flawless, airbrushed finish with this set of three soft, latex-free makeup sponges. The unique teardrop shape allows for precise application in hard-to-reach areas, while the damp sponge blends makeup seamlessly for a natural, skin-like finish. Expands when wet for maximum coverage.

name: Matte Liquid Lipstick Collection
description: Experience bold, long-lasting color with this collection of ultra-pigmented liquid lipsticks. The lightweight formula dries to a comfortable matte finish that won't feather or transfer. Includes five stunning shades ranging from everyday nudes to statement reds.

name: Illuminating Face Primer
description: Prep your skin for flawless makeup application with this light-reflecting primer. The silky formula smooths over pores and fine lines while adding a subtle glow that makes skin look radiant and refreshed. Infused with hydrating ingredients to keep your complexion comfortable all day.

name: Full Coverage Concealer
description: Instantly erase dark circles, blemishes, and imperfections with this creamy, high-coverage concealer. The lightweight formula blends seamlessly and won't crease or cake, providing a natural-looking finish that lasts all day. Available in a wide range of shades to match every skin tone.

name: Glitter Eye Shadow Palette
description: Add sparkle to your look with this dazzling palette of 12 glitter-packed shades. The creamy, highly pigmented shadows apply smoothly and stay put without fallout. Mix and match colors to create endless eye-catching looks for day or night.

name: Lengthening & Curling Mascara
description: Get dramatic length and lift with this innovative mascara that curls as it lengthens. The curved brush reaches every lash, while the buildable formula adds volume without clumping. Infused with conditioning ingredients to keep lashes soft and healthy.

name: Lip Plumping Gloss
description: Enhance your pout with this lip-plumping gloss that delivers instant volume and a tingling sensation. The sheer, glossy formula provides hydration and a subtle hint of color while making lips appear fuller and more defined. Perfect for everyday wear or special occasions.

name: Professional Makeup Brush Set
description: Elevate your makeup game with this 12-piece professional brush set. Each brush is crafted with ultra-soft synthetic bristles for flawless application and blending. Includes brushes for face, eyes, and lips, plus a sleek carrying case for storage and travel.

name: Color-Changing Lip Balm
description: Treat your lips to this innovative balm that adjusts to your unique pH for a custom pink hue. Enriched with nourishing oils and vitamin E, it provides long-lasting hydration while enhancing your natural lip color. The sheer, buildable finish is perfect for any occasion.

name: Bronzing Powder Duo
description: Get a natural, sun-kissed glow with this bronzing powder duo featuring both matte and shimmer finishes. The finely milled powders blend seamlessly onto skin for a warm, radiant look. Use alone or together to customize your bronzed effect.

name: Eyebrow Pomade & Brush
description: Define and fill your brows with this long-lasting pomade that glides on smoothly and sets to a waterproof finish. The creamy formula allows for precise application, creating natural-looking hair-like strokes. Includes a dual-ended brush for easy shaping and blending.

name: Dewy Finish Setting Spray
description: Lock in your makeup while adding a fresh, dewy glow with this hydrating setting spray. The ultra-fine mist extends makeup wear and gives skin a luminous, healthy-looking finish. Infused with skin-loving ingredients to keep your complexion comfortable and radiant all day.

name: Satin Finish Lipstick Trio
description: Experience luxurious color with this trio of satin-finish lipsticks. The creamy formula glides on effortlessly, delivering rich pigment with a soft sheen that's neither too matte nor too glossy. Includes three universally flattering shades for everyday glamour.

name: Glow Boosting Face Serum
description: Prep your skin for makeup with this illuminating serum that instantly brightens and hydrates. The lightweight formula absorbs quickly, leaving skin with a subtle radiance that enhances any foundation. Packed with antioxidants and vitamins for long-term skin health.

name: Volumizing Lip Liner Set
description: Define your lips with precision using this set of three creamy lip liners. The smooth formula prevents feathering and provides the perfect base for lipstick or gloss. Includes nude, pink, and red shades to complement any lip color.

name: Colorful Eyeliner Collection
description: Make a statement with this collection of five vibrant, highly pigmented eyeliners. Each liner features a felt-tip applicator for precise, easy application. Create bold graphic looks or subtle pops of color with these long-lasting, smudge-proof formulas.

name: Pore Minimizing Face Primer
description: Create a smooth canvas for makeup with this mattifying primer that instantly blurs the appearance of pores and fine lines. The lightweight gel formula controls oil and shine throughout the day, ensuring your makeup stays fresh and flawless from morning to night.

name: Sculpting Contour Stick
description: Chisel and define your features with this easy-to-use contour stick. The creamy formula blends seamlessly into skin for a natural-looking shadow that adds dimension to your face. Perfect for on-the-go touch-ups and beginner-friendly contouring.

name: Magnetic False Lashes Kit
description: Achieve dramatic lashes instantly with this innovative magnetic lash system. No glue requiredâ€”the magnetic liner and lashes snap together securely for all-day wear. Includes two pairs of reusable lashes and a magnetic eyeliner pen for easy application.

name: Liquid Shimmer Eye Shadow
description: Add instant glamour to your eyes with this liquid shimmer shadow that dries to a long-lasting, crease-proof finish. The buildable formula allows you to create subtle shimmer or intense sparkle. Available in six stunning shades perfect for day or night.

name: Tinted Moisturizer with SPF
description: Simplify your routine with this multi-tasking tinted moisturizer that provides sheer coverage, hydration, and SPF 30 sun protection. The lightweight formula evens out skin tone while letting your natural beauty shine through. Perfect for no-makeup makeup days.

name: Eye Primer Potion
description: Make your eye makeup last all day with this powerful eye primer. The lightweight formula smooths over lids, prevents creasing, and intensifies the color of your eye shadows. Creates the perfect base for any eye look, from natural to dramatic.

name: Matte & Glow Highlighter Duo
description: Get the best of both worlds with this highlighter duo featuring matte and shimmer finishes. The matte side adds subtle definition, while the shimmer side creates a radiant glow. Use separately or blend together for a customized highlighting effect.

name: Lip Scrub & Balm Duo
description: Pamper your lips with this exfoliating scrub and nourishing balm duo. The sugar scrub gently buffs away dry, flaky skin, while the ultra-hydrating balm locks in moisture for soft, smooth lips. The perfect prep for any lip color.

name: Cream Eye Shadow Stick Set
description: Get effortless eye looks with this set of three cream shadow sticks. The twist-up design allows for easy, mess-free application, while the creamy formula blends smoothly and sets to a long-lasting finish. Includes neutral, bronze, and plum shades.

name: Powder Brush Cleaner Mat
description: Keep your brushes clean and bacteria-free with this textured silicone mat. The raised ridges and suction cups make it easy to deep clean brushes with soap and water. Extends the life of your brushes while ensuring flawless makeup application every time.

name: BB Cream Multi-Benefit Formula
description: Simplify your beauty routine with this all-in-one BB cream that moisturizes, primes, and provides lightweight coverage. The buildable formula evens out skin tone while SPF protects from sun damage. Infused with antioxidants for healthy, radiant skin.

name: Pressed Pigment Eye Shadow
description: Create vibrant eye looks with this highly pigmented pressed shadow. The buttery formula applies smoothly and blends effortlessly for intense color payoff. Available in bold shades perfect for creative makeup looks and special occasions.

name: Makeup Organizer Caddy
description: Keep your beauty essentials organized and accessible with this multi-compartment makeup organizer. Features adjustable dividers and a rotating base for easy access to all your products. The sleek design looks beautiful on any vanity or bathroom counter.

name: Baking Powder For Undereyes
description: Set your under-eye concealer with this ultra-fine baking powder that brightens and prevents creasing. The translucent formula works on all skin tones, creating a flawless, photo-ready finish. Perfect for special events or everyday wear.

name: Face Powder Brush Large
description: Apply powder products with precision using this ultra-soft, densely packed brush. The large dome shape picks up just the right amount of product and distributes it evenly for a seamless finish. Works perfectly with setting powder, bronzer, or blush.

name: Gloss To Matte Lip Transformer
description: Transform any lip color from glossy to matte with this innovative finishing powder. Simply apply your favorite lipstick or gloss, then dust on this translucent powder for an instant matte finish. Keeps color locked in place without the drying effect.

name: Eye Makeup Remover Pads
description: Gently remove even the most stubborn waterproof makeup with these pre-soaked remover pads. The oil-free formula won't leave a greasy residue and is gentle enough for sensitive skin. Each pad is infused with soothing botanicals to cleanse and condition lashes.

name: Sparkle Body Shimmer Oil
description: Add an all-over glow with this luxurious shimmer oil that catches the light beautifully. The non-greasy formula absorbs quickly while leaving skin with a subtle sparkle. Perfect for highlighting collarbones, shoulders, and legs for special occasions.

name: Mini Makeup Palette Travel Set
description: Take your makeup on the go with this compact all-in-one palette. Includes eye shadows, blush, bronzer, and lip colors in a convenient portable size. The magnetic closure keeps everything secure, making it perfect for travel or touch-ups throughout the day.

name: Foundation Mixing Drops
description: Customize your foundation shade with these pigment drops. Add to any foundation to adjust the depth and undertone for a perfect match year-round. Available in light, medium, and dark shades to accommodate seasonal skin tone changes.

name: Lash Primer Conditioning Base
description: Boost your mascara performance with this lash primer that conditions and lengthens. The white formula grips onto lashes, creating the perfect base for mascara application. Infused with conditioning ingredients to promote lash health and prevent breakage.

name: Eyebrow Stencil Kit
description: Achieve perfectly shaped brows with this eyebrow stencil kit featuring four different arch shapes. The reusable stencils make it easy to create symmetrical, professional-looking brows at home. Includes a detailed guide for selecting the right shape for your face.

name: Face Mist Refreshing Spray
description: Refresh and hydrate your skin throughout the day with this cooling face mist. The ultra-fine spray delivers a burst of moisture and can be used to prep skin before makeup or set makeup for a dewy finish. Infused with botanical extracts and vitamins.

name: Lighted Makeup Mirror Compact
description: See every detail with this LED lighted compact mirror. The bright, natural light ensures flawless makeup application even in low-light conditions. The compact size makes it perfect for travel or touch-ups on the go. Includes a regular and 2x magnifying mirror.

name: Makeup Melting Cleansing Balm
description: Effortlessly remove all traces of makeup with this luxurious cleansing balm. The solid balm melts into an oil upon contact with skin, dissolving even waterproof makeup. Rinses clean without leaving a greasy residue, leaving skin soft and nourished.

name: Color Correcting Primer Palette
description: Address multiple skin concerns with this color correcting primer palette. Green neutralizes redness, lavender brightens dullness, peach corrects dark circles, and yellow evens out skin tone. Use alone or under foundation for a flawless complexion.

name: Soft Focus Blurring Powder
description: Achieve an airbrushed finish with this light-diffusing powder that instantly blurs imperfections. The translucent formula minimizes the appearance of pores and fine lines while controlling shine. Can be worn alone or over makeup for a soft-focus effect.

name: Tweezer & Scissors Beauty Set
description: Maintain perfectly groomed brows with this essential tool set. Includes precision slant tweezers for easy hair removal and small scissors for trimming. Both tools feature stainless steel construction for durability and come in a protective case.

name: Lip Oil Treatment Gloss
description: Nourish and beautify your lips with this ultra-hydrating lip oil. The lightweight formula provides a glossy sheen while deeply moisturizing with natural oils and vitamin E. Available in clear or lightly tinted shades for a healthy, natural look.

name: Silicone Makeup Sponge
description: Experience mess-free makeup application with this innovative silicone sponge. Unlike traditional sponges, it doesn't absorb product, so you use less foundation. The smooth surface glides over skin for an even, streak-free finish. Easy to clean and lasts for years.

name: Face Highlighter Stick Trio
description: Illuminate your complexion with this highlighter stick trio featuring champagne, rose gold, and golden shades. The creamy formula glides on smoothly and blends seamlessly for a natural-looking glow. Perfect for highlighting cheekbones, brow bones, and cupid's bow.

name: Clear Brow & Lash Gel
description: Keep your brows and lashes in place all day with this clear, non-flaking gel. The lightweight formula tames unruly hairs and adds subtle definition without stiffness or crunchiness. Can be worn alone or over brow products and mascara.

name: Blending Brush Professional
description: Achieve seamless eye looks with this ultra-soft blending brush. The fluffy, dome-shaped bristles effortlessly diffuse harsh lines and blend colors for a professional finish. Essential for creating gradient effects and perfecting your eye makeup technique.

name: Liquid Liner Stamp & Pen
description: Create perfect winged liner in seconds with this innovative stamp and pen duo. The stamp ensures symmetrical wings every time, while the pen allows for customization and touch-ups. The long-lasting formula stays put without smudging or fading.

name: Mattifying Oil Control Primer
description: Keep shine at bay with this oil-absorbing primer that creates a smooth, matte base for makeup. The lightweight gel formula minimizes the appearance of pores and extends makeup wear for up to 12 hours. Perfect for oily and combination skin types.

name: Makeup Bag Travel Organizer
description: Keep your beauty essentials organized with this spacious makeup bag featuring multiple compartments and pockets. The waterproof interior protects against spills, while the durable exterior withstands daily use. Perfect for travel or everyday organization.

name: Cushion Foundation Compact
description: Experience lightweight coverage with this innovative cushion foundation. The built-in sponge applicator delivers a natural, dewy finish while the compact design makes it perfect for on-the-go application. Includes SPF for sun protection and comes with a refill.

name: Lip Liner Sharpener Duo
description: Keep your lip and eye liners perfectly sharp with this dual sharpener. Features two sizes to accommodate standard and jumbo pencils. The built-in cleaning pick removes excess product, while the clear lid catches shavings for mess-free sharpening.

name: Cheek & Lip Cream Stain
description: Add a natural flush to your cheeks and lips with this buildable cream stain. The long-lasting formula provides a soft matte finish that looks like you're naturally flushed. The convenient stick format makes application quick and easy.

name: Makeup Brush Cleaning Spray
description: Quickly clean and sanitize your makeup brushes with this antibacterial spray. The fast-drying formula removes makeup residue and kills bacteria without damaging brush bristles. Perfect for spot cleaning between deep washes or for on-the-go touch-ups.

name: Glow Drops Illuminating Serum
description: Mix these concentrated glow drops with your foundation or moisturizer for a customizable radiant finish. The liquid highlighter formula contains light-reflecting particles that give skin a natural, lit-from-within glow. Can also be used alone on high points of the face.

name: Kabuki Buffing Brush
description: Achieve a flawless finish with this dense kabuki brush perfect for buffing foundation, powder, or bronzer. The soft, synthetic bristles pick up the right amount of product and blend it seamlessly into skin. The short handle provides maximum control.

name: Eyeshadow Shield Protectors
description: Prevent fallout and protect your under-eye area with these disposable eyeshadow shields. The curved design fits comfortably under the eye, catching excess shadow and glitter. Makes cleanup easy and ensures a flawless finish. Pack of 50 shields.

name: Lip Stain Marker Pen
description: Get long-lasting lip color with this innovative marker pen. The felt tip applicator provides precise, even coverage that dries to a comfortable stain. The buildable formula allows you to create your desired intensity, from sheer to bold.

name: Contour Powder Palette
description: Sculpt and define your features with this versatile contour powder palette. Includes three shades for contouring, bronzing, and highlighting. The finely milled powders blend seamlessly for a natural-looking dimension. Suitable for all skin tones.

name: Eyelash Curler Tool
description: Open up your eyes with this precision eyelash curler that creates a natural-looking curl. The ergonomic design ensures comfortable use, while the silicone pads protect lashes from damage. Includes two replacement pads for long-lasting performance.

name: Holographic Highlighter Palette
description: Create an ethereal glow with this holographic highlighter palette featuring four iridescent shades. The buttery formula delivers intense shine with just one swipe. Perfect for festival looks or adding dimension to everyday makeup.

name: Lip Exfoliating Mask Patches
description: Pamper your lips with these hydrating exfoliating mask patches. Each patch is infused with nourishing ingredients that gently remove dead skin while moisturizing. Leave lips soft, smooth, and ready for any lip color. Pack of 10 treatments.

name: Face Tanning Drops
description: Achieve a sun-kissed glow without sun exposure using these customizable face tanning drops. Mix with your moisturizer or serum to create your desired tan depth. The streak-free formula develops gradually for a natural-looking bronze that fades evenly.

name: Airbrush Foundation Spray
description: Get a flawless airbrushed finish at home with this lightweight foundation spray. The ultra-fine mist delivers buildable coverage that looks natural and feels comfortable. The long-wearing formula resists transfer and stays fresh all day.

name: Makeup Removing Towelettes
description: Remove your makeup quickly and easily with these ultra-soft cleansing towelettes. Each wipe is pre-moistened with a gentle formula that dissolves makeup, dirt, and oil without harsh rubbing. Perfect for travel or when you're too tired for a full cleansing routine. Pack of 30.

name: Micellar Cleansing Water
description: Gently remove makeup and impurities with this no-rinse micellar water. The micelle molecules attract dirt and makeup like a magnet, lifting them away without harsh rubbing. Suitable for all skin types including sensitive skin. Leaves no residue.

name: Precision Shader Brush Set
description: Perfect your eye makeup with this set of three shader brushes in different sizes. The flat, dense bristles pack on color with precision and are ideal for applying shadow to the lid and lower lash line. Essential tools for creating any eye look.

name: Reusable False Lash Applicator
description: Apply false lashes with ease using this innovative applicator tool. The ergonomic design provides a secure grip on lashes while you position them perfectly along your lash line. No more struggling with tweezers or sticky fingers. Works with strip and individual lashes.

name: Neon Eye Shadow Palette
description: Make a bold statement with this vibrant neon eyeshadow palette featuring 10 electric shades. The highly pigmented formulas apply smoothly and blend effortlessly for eye-catching looks. Perfect for festivals, parties, or anyone who loves to experiment with color.

name: Vitamin C Primer Serum
description: Brighten your complexion while prepping for makeup with this vitamin C-infused primer serum. The silky formula smooths skin texture, evens tone, and provides antioxidant protection. Creates the perfect canvas for flawless makeup application.

name: Brow Gel With Fibers
description: Fill in sparse brows with this tinted brow gel infused with hair-like fibers. The buildable formula adds volume and definition while holding hairs in place. Creates the appearance of fuller, thicker brows that look completely natural.

name: Velvet Matte Lip Crayon
description: Experience luxurious color with this jumbo lip crayon. The creamy formula glides on smoothly and dries to a comfortable matte finish. The precision tip allows for easy application without a liner. Available in a range of flattering shades.

name: Under Eye Color Corrector
description: Banish dark circles with this peachy color corrector specifically designed for the under-eye area. The creamy formula neutralizes blue and purple tones while providing hydration. Wear alone or under concealer for brighter, more awake-looking eyes.
